&lt;h2 id="前言">前言&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://moyf.github.io/hugo-stack-blog/hugo-stack-blog/p/blender-%E6%A8%A1%E5%9E%8B%E6%80%8E%E4%B9%88%E5%AF%BC%E5%85%A5-unreal/Assets/Pasted-image-20230627172104.png"
width="308"
height="243"
loading="lazy"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="126"
data-flex-basis="304px"
>&lt;br>
导入进去之后材质会丢掉，怎么会是呢？&lt;/p>
&lt;p>参考这个教程：&lt;br>
&lt;div class="video-wrapper">
&lt;iframe loading="lazy"
src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/N8y_eH7QB2o"
allowfullscreen
title="YouTube Video"
>
&lt;/iframe>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/p>
&lt;blockquote>
&lt;p>&lt;a class="link" href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=N8y_eH7QB2o" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
>油管地址&lt;/a>&lt;/p>
&lt;/blockquote>
&lt;p>先选 Export 然后选择 &lt;code>.fbx&lt;/code> 格式；&lt;/p>
&lt;h2 id="blender-里的纹理">Blender 里的纹理&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>SketchFab 下载过来的模型是分开的，导入 Blender 会显示白模。&lt;br>
怎么把纹理贴图重新加回去呢？&lt;/p>
&lt;p>要用到插件 &lt;code>Node Wrangler&lt;/code> ；&lt;/p>
&lt;p>首先导入模型，然后打开 Shading 界面：&lt;br>
&lt;img src="https://moyf.github.io/hugo-stack-blog/hugo-stack-blog/p/blender-%E6%A8%A1%E5%9E%8B%E6%80%8E%E4%B9%88%E5%AF%BC%E5%85%A5-unreal/Assets/Pasted-image-20230710181041.png"
width="320"
height="52"
loading="lazy"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="615"
data-flex-basis="1476px"
>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>选中物体，右边的属性界面切到材质：&lt;br>
&lt;img src="https://moyf.github.io/hugo-stack-blog/hugo-stack-blog/p/blender-%E6%A8%A1%E5%9E%8B%E6%80%8E%E4%B9%88%E5%AF%BC%E5%85%A5-unreal/Assets/Pasted-image-20230710181119.png"
width="454"
height="528"
loading="lazy"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="85"
data-flex-basis="206px"
>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>如果没有的话就先按加号新建一个；&lt;/p>
&lt;p>然后在着色器窗口能看到两个节点，&lt;br>
&lt;img src="https://moyf.github.io/hugo-stack-blog/hugo-stack-blog/p/blender-%E6%A8%A1%E5%9E%8B%E6%80%8E%E4%B9%88%E5%AF%BC%E5%85%A5-unreal/Assets/Pasted-image-20230710181309.png"
width="642"
height="650"
loading="lazy"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="98"
data-flex-basis="237px"
>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>选中 Principled BSDF，然后按快捷键 &lt;code>Ctrl+Shfit+T&lt;/code>；&lt;br>
在打开的窗口中全选材质图片：&lt;br>
&lt;img src="https://moyf.github.io/hugo-stack-blog/hugo-stack-blog/p/blender-%E6%A8%A1%E5%9E%8B%E6%80%8E%E4%B9%88%E5%AF%BC%E5%85%A5-unreal/Assets/Pasted-image-20230710181332.png"
width="331"
height="137"
loading="lazy"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="241"
data-flex-basis="579px"
>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>插件就会自动创建好各个节点：&lt;br>
&lt;img src="https://moyf.github.io/hugo-stack-blog/hugo-stack-blog/p/blender-%E6%A8%A1%E5%9E%8B%E6%80%8E%E4%B9%88%E5%AF%BC%E5%85%A5-unreal/Assets/Pasted-image-20230710181400.png"
width="1548"
height="1203"
loading="lazy"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="128"
data-flex-basis="308px"
>&lt;/p>
&lt;h2 id="打包纹理">打包纹理&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>导出-&amp;gt;fbx 格式：&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;code>Path Mode&lt;/code> 选成 &lt;strong>Copy&lt;/strong>：&lt;br>
&lt;img src="https://moyf.github.io/hugo-stack-blog/hugo-stack-blog/p/blender-%E6%A8%A1%E5%9E%8B%E6%80%8E%E4%B9%88%E5%AF%BC%E5%85%A5-unreal/Assets/Pasted-image-20230627170606.png"
width="322"
height="175"
loading="lazy"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="184"
data-flex-basis="441px"
>&lt;br>
然后勾选边上的 &lt;code>Embed Textures&lt;/code> 按钮：&lt;br>
&lt;img src="https://moyf.github.io/hugo-stack-blog/hugo-stack-blog/p/blender-%E6%A8%A1%E5%9E%8B%E6%80%8E%E4%B9%88%E5%AF%BC%E5%85%A5-unreal/Assets/Pasted-image-20230627170707.png"
width="365"
height="151"
loading="lazy"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="241"
data-flex-basis="580px"
>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>这样才能把纹理一起打包进去。&lt;/p>
&lt;h2 id="限定范围">限定范围&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>东西多的话可以只勾选 &lt;code>Selected Objects&lt;/code>，然后下面也可以只选 &lt;code>Mesh&lt;/code>：&lt;br>
&lt;img src="https://moyf.github.io/hugo-stack-blog/hugo-stack-blog/p/blender-%E6%A8%A1%E5%9E%8B%E6%80%8E%E4%B9%88%E5%AF%BC%E5%85%A5-unreal/Assets/Pasted-image-20230627170827.png"
width="238"
height="259"
loading="lazy"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="91"
data-flex-basis="220px"
>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>这样可以避免把相机和灯光啥的一起导出。&lt;/p>
&lt;blockquote>
&lt;p>——底下这个 Mesh 可能得小心，好像会导致啥都没导出来。&lt;/p>
&lt;/blockquote>
&lt;p>导出之后可以预览&lt;/p>
&lt;h2 id="轴向">轴向&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://moyf.github.io/hugo-stack-blog/hugo-stack-blog/p/blender-%E6%A8%A1%E5%9E%8B%E6%80%8E%E4%B9%88%E5%AF%BC%E5%85%A5-unreal/Assets/Pasted-image-20231222173650.png"
width="730"
height="259"
loading="lazy"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="281"
data-flex-basis="676px"
>&lt;br>
&lt;a class="link" href="https://www.reddit.com/r/unrealengine/comments/kw2v88/newbie_blender_to_ue4_settings_and_how_to_get/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
>newbie: Blender to UE4 settings and how to get objects oriented on the right axis : unrealengine&lt;/a>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>详见下方 &lt;a class="link" href="#%e5%9d%90%e6%a0%87%e8%bd%b4%e6%ad%aa%e4%ba%86%ef%bc%9f" >坐标轴歪了？&lt;/a> 章节。&lt;/p>
&lt;h2 id="平滑">平滑？&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://moyf.github.io/hugo-stack-blog/hugo-stack-blog/p/blender-%E6%A8%A1%E5%9E%8B%E6%80%8E%E4%B9%88%E5%AF%BC%E5%85%A5-unreal/Assets/Pasted-image-20230627171011.png"
width="230"
height="153"
loading="lazy"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="150"
data-flex-basis="360px"
>&lt;br>
视频里说这里也可以把 &lt;code>Smoothing&lt;/code> 改成 &lt;code>Face&lt;/code>，但我不太明白，先不动。&lt;/p>
&lt;h2 id="保存导出预设">保存导出预设&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://moyf.github.io/hugo-stack-blog/hugo-stack-blog/p/blender-%E6%A8%A1%E5%9E%8B%E6%80%8E%E4%B9%88%E5%AF%BC%E5%85%A5-unreal/Assets/Pasted-image-20230627171434.png"
width="237"
height="97"
loading="lazy"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="244"
data-flex-basis="586px"
>&lt;br>
完事儿可以存成一个 Preset 方便复用。&lt;/p>
&lt;h2 id="坐标轴歪了">坐标轴歪了？&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>&lt;a class="link" href="https://blog.csdn.net/jxyyl/article/details/120328702" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
>Blender模型导出到ue4_blender骨骼导入ue方向问题_三尺三的博客-CSDN博客&lt;/a>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>blender：&lt;br>
将模型面朝X轴放置，清除旋转与缩放。&lt;br>
&lt;img src="https://moyf.github.io/hugo-stack-blog/hugo-stack-blog/p/blender-%E6%A8%A1%E5%9E%8B%E6%80%8E%E4%B9%88%E5%AF%BC%E5%85%A5-unreal/Assets/Pasted-image-20230627171639.png"
width="782"
height="532"
loading="lazy"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="146"
data-flex-basis="352px"
>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;mark>⭐️重要：单位改成 0.01：&lt;/mark>&lt;br>
&lt;img src="https://moyf.github.io/hugo-stack-blog/hugo-stack-blog/p/blender-%E6%A8%A1%E5%9E%8B%E6%80%8E%E4%B9%88%E5%AF%BC%E5%85%A5-unreal/Assets/Pasted-image-20230627171818.png"
width="440"
height="265"
loading="lazy"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="166"
data-flex-basis="398px"
>&lt;br>
可能因为 UE 里是 0.01 米等于一个单位？&lt;/p>
&lt;p>导出的时候：&lt;/p>
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>Forward 选择 &lt;code>-Y Forward&lt;/code>&lt;/li>
&lt;li>Up 选择 &lt;code>Z Up&lt;/code>&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;p>&lt;style type="text/css">.notice{--root-color:#444;--root-background:#eff;--title-color:#fff;--title-background:#7bd;--warning-title:#c33;--warning-content:#fee;--info-title:#fb7;--info-content:#fec;--note-title:#6be;--note-content:#e7f2fa;--tip-title:#5a5;--tip-content:#efe}@media (prefers-color-scheme:dark){.notice{--root-color:#ddd;--root-background:#eff;--title-color:#fff;--title-background:#7bd;--warning-title:#800;--warning-content:#400;--info-title:#a50;--info-content:#420;--note-title:#069;--note-content:#023;--tip-title:#363;--tip-content:#121}}body.dark .notice{--root-color:#ddd;--root-background:#eff;--title-color:#fff;--title-background:#7bd;--warning-title:#800;--warning-content:#400;--info-title:#a50;--info-content:#420;--note-title:#069;--note-content:#023;--tip-title:#363;--tip-content:#121}.notice{padding:18px;line-height:24px;margin-bottom:24px;border-radius:4px;color:var(--root-color);background:var(--root-background)}.notice p:last-child{margin-bottom:0}.notice-title{margin:-18px -18px 12px;padding:4px 18px;border-radius:4px 4px 0 0;font-weight:700;color:var(--title-color);background:var(--title-background)}.notice.warning .notice-title{background:var(--warning-title)}.notice.warning{background:var(--warning-content)}.notice.info .notice-title{background:var(--info-title)}.notice.info{background:var(--info-content)}.notice.note .notice-title{background:var(--note-title)}.notice.note{background:var(--note-content)}.notice.tip .notice-title{background:var(--tip-title)}.notice.tip{background:var(--tip-content)}.icon-notice{display:inline-flex;align-self:center;margin-right:8px}.icon-notice img,.icon-notice svg{height:1em;width:1em;fill:currentColor}.icon-notice img,.icon-notice.baseline svg{top:.125em;position:relative}&lt;/style>
